        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I've never played anywhere but Rallos, and wouldn't think of leaving.  As far as I know we're the only PVP server that still has item loot, meaning if you kill someone, you get all their coin AND get to loot one of their items.  Sux when ya lose, but you can make/save a lot of money that way too ; )  </P><P>As far as the suggestion of playing a wizard, PFFT, maybe if you wanna ebay one with MB.  There are certain lvl ranges where wizards rule, just like there are certain lvl ranges where any class will rule, but honestly I have not once been killed by a wizard since getting deflux, and I've been jumped by plenty.  They think they can pop in and nuke ppl to death, and vs a necro it just doesnt work.  You can get off 2 200 point (with pvp reduction) lifetaps for every 1 nuke they hit you with. With a little bit of resist gear gaining you partials, you'll come out ahead every time, without ever using a DOT. The only time wizards were bad vs a necro were in the 30's - 40's, and at low levels.  Honestly at the high lvls a necro is still one of the best PVP classes.  Mid 20's/early 30's we shine, then we're toward the bottom again till the 50's, when we get back on top.  </P><P>The other classes I would suggest are SK, Druid and Bard.  Get an SK a shit-hot weapon and some lvl's (spells) and he's a force to be reckoned with.  Droods have a snare that is resisted FAR less than our darkness, and can kite you and your pet around all day.  Once they get Winged Death they're nasty as hell.  I eat most mages alive, but RUN from epic mages, however I see druids drop em all the time.  Bards are good for pure survivability.  They don't dish out a lot of damage, but good luck actually killing one.  I despise bards.  </P><P>Like someone said above, Rangers are pretty gimp until into the 50's.  Archery can be HELL at high lvls, but for the most part a "pk ranger" is a joke.   </P><P></P><P><img src="http://www.onethirtyeight.com/graphics-2/cg.gif"><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
