         Depends completely on the level range you are aiming for. A level 60 Ranger AA'd out the ass OWNS all.  With resists the way they are, snare is gonna land.  I've only played pvp servers, am now on SZ and love it.  I am of course a necro.  The all time great pvp ganker is Wizard without a doubt, and with POP they will only be more so.  Deflux and any lifetap against a wizzie is the wrong approach.  Especially if they are an epic wiz.  Just use your best dots (even though now those are pretty easily resisted) and BOD/Vexing if you got it and play the range game or HS.  Dont even try to tap unless you get them dispelled - it's a waste of mana.  If they aren't epic'd you have a much better chance with taps.</P><P>Any caster pretty much owns with the resists all screwed to hell, including hybrids.  Just dont play on sullon zek if you can't stomach lvl 60 druids, rangers etc coming to your lvl 10 xp grounds and griefing you, cuz it happens.</P><P>Fermunda <Hate> </P><P>Sullon Zek<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
